    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs smoothly and looks great on the road. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
