    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies to deliver 333 hp with a sharp, linear throttle response. The power is managed by a traditional Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a limited-slip M-differential. This vehicle has been mechanically sorted with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, addressing the primary technical concerns of the chassis. The suspension remains composed with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and turn-in precision. While it shows light cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for an owner seeking peak E46 performance without the premium of a garage queen.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
