    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2016 Porsche Macan S in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver, balancing performance with utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel reflect its honest road history. Inside, the black leather interior is in excellent shape; the bolsters show minimal wear, and all electronics\u2014including the premium Bose sound system and navigation\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this Macan is sound. I have adhered strictly to the manufacturer's service schedule, with the most recent major service completed just four months ago, including new spark plugs and a brake fluid flush. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last year. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly through the PDK gearbox, and offers a tight, responsive feel. It is a complete package for a discerning owner who values a well-documented service history and a car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
